Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:37.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}縱使相互呼喚未曾停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:46.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}卻入歧途 眼見漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:57.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}相互吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:04.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}相互追逐的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:12.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}相對而生的兩極 紛繁演化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:16.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}孕育世間萬物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:23.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}正因有你 方得有我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:28.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}縱兩相隔 亦在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:29.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)\an1}在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:35.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}世間眾生皆非完美無瑕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:42.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}而所欠缺的那重要部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:49.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(20,60)}只能不住追尋
